data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ** APPROVED SELLER CREDIT ** This home is eligible for a 2/1 INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN financed by a seller credit. Perfect Florida Getaway! This 4-bedroom boasts an open floor plan that welcomes natural light, creating a warm and inviting home. The heart of the home is designed for seamless living, making it perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The open kitchen offers granite countertops, a huge island, and stainless steel appliances. Step onto the spacious screened porch and experience the best of indoor-outdoor living. Located in the heart of Kissimmee and minutes from Lake Nona, you'll have easy access to all the amenities and attractions the area has to offer. Don't let this opportunity slip away – schedule a viewing today!
